{"tid":1642020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［文宣戰］正式向藍絲PAGE發動文宣戰","createTime":"2019-10-09T14:09:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T11:00:46.000Z","uid":50502,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0e05d9809ec720c35f27d3aba9be75dcb581019c","tid":1642020,"uid":50502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:09:50.000Z","msg":"發放文宣比淺藍/深藍最有效係深入敵陣 <br />\n<strong>係一個40萬藍絲like既page post一張文宣 可以比係街派十張文宣單更有用<br />\n</strong><br />\n以下page等於藍絲中既連登 有電話既都會上 可以直接將文宣reach到藍絲<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">港人講地</span> (45萬follow)</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/speakouthk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fspeakouthk%2F&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX5%2BNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=edabc79c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/speakouthk/</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">HKG報 HKGpao</span> (30萬follow)</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkgpaocom/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkgpaocom%2F&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX5%2BNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=62f0e01b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkgpaocom/</a><br />\n<br />\n唔洗一定逐個post反駁 只要逐個post發放文宣圖<strong> <span style=\"color: red;\">互like手足既post推上熱門回覆</span></strong> 比藍絲知道香港發生緊咩事 激到深藍爆血管都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家個page冇咩手足理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n懇求大家一齊入去post爆文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">向藍絲文宣戰，正式啟動。</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"6a7ec58847e21f81caa2cc1246dcef95748354ac","tid":1642020,"uid":50502,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T14:12:19.000Z","msg":"文宣(多圖):<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1625161/page/1\" targ